Testing page elements¶

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

square = np.random.randn(100, 100)
wide = np.random.randn(100, 1000)

Hiding inputs¶

# Hide input
square = np.random.randn(100, 100)
wide = np.random.randn(100, 1000)

fig, ax = plt.subplots()
ax.imshow(square)

fig, ax = plt.subplots()
ax.imshow(wide)
